{
  "stem": "9262.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in order to go to the small, little places, they had to go to the big towns first.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had to be repatriated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As we were already in Silesia, it wasn't very far from people who came from the Silesia region to go to Katowice, which was a big town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a big town and had a large, Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we came out from the railway station, they had the carriages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't have motorcars in those days, only a few motorcars in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was mainly a horse and carriage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we gave the destination, which was Gdanska 28.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in those days, most of the-- what are they called in English, these-- fellow who drive-- coach drivers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of them were Jewish, and while they were driving us to our destination, they said, who has done this to you?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "May he burn in hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "May he never come to our place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "May he never come to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So little did we know that he would follow us very soon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, there was great jubilation when we arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my aunts and my uncles, they were already well informed in advance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we stayed with my uncle overnight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The following morning, we were billeted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My brothers went to other cousins, other uncles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- so we were distributed, between one family to the other family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And who were you with?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was staying with my father, mother, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we were staying with my uncle, who had a son who was the same age as myself.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After one week, my uncle found us accommodation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We moved out and we had a two and half room apartment in the center of town.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
